	<h1 class="title">怎么删 iOS 设备上的原生应用？今后系统可能要帮你自动隐藏了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3910/small/3910.png?1418028195" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐怡园 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-07 13:06:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25106/medium/25106.jpg?1460004793" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="25106" data-title="《怎么删 iOS 设备上的原生应用？今后系统可能要帮你自动隐藏了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25106/medium/25106.jpg?1460004793" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25106.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
